## Information Hierarchy

### **Visual Hierarchy Techniques**

#### **1. Size & Weight**
- Most important content gets largest size
- Use font weight to create emphasis without increasing size
- Maintain maximum 3-4 hierarchy levels per page

#### **2. Color & Contrast**
- High contrast for primary content
- Reduced contrast for secondary information
- Never rely on color alone for hierarchy

#### **3. Spacing & Positioning**
- More spacing around important elements
- Group related information together
- Use white space to create focus

#### **4. Content Structure**
```html
<!-- Article Page Structure -->
<article>
  <header>
    <h1>Primary Headline</h1>
    <p class="metadata">Date, Author, Categories</p>
  </header>
  
  <section class="content">
    <p class="lead">Opening paragraph with larger text</p>
    <p>Body content...</p>
  </section>
  
  <footer>
    <div class="actions">Secondary actions</div>
  </footer>
</article>
```

