## Navigation & Wayfinding

### **Primary Navigation**
- **Maximum 7 items** in main navigation (cognitive limit)
- **Clear, descriptive labels** (avoid clever/cute names)
- **Active state indication** shows current location
- **Consistent placement** across all pages

### **Breadcrumbs**
```html
<nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
  <ol class="breadcrumb">
    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="/learn">Learn</a></li>
    <li aria-current="page">Quiz Results</li>
  </ol>
</nav>
```

### **Search Interface**
- **Prominent placement** (top-right preferred)
- **Predictive suggestions** when possible
- **Clear search results** with filtering options
- **"No results" state** with helpful suggestions

